# File: app/styles/print.css.ab
# Purpose: Empty Compass print media stylesheet placeholder stored in app/styles/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
An empty CSS file serving as the Compass placeholder for print media styles. Contains only the standard Compass generator comment instructing how to import it for print media (`<link href="..." media="print">`). No actual print-specific styles have been defined. This is the older `app/styles/` location equivalent of `app/assets/css/print.css`.

## Interface
No exports. Empty placeholder stylesheet.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies.

## Implementation Notes
- 1 line — only the Compass welcome comment, no actual CSS rules
- Generated by the Yeoman Angular generator's Compass scaffold
- No print styles have been authored for the TuyoTools frontend
- Counterpart: `app/assets/css/print.css` (also empty, with a CSS source map reference)
